Class ShieldPowerUp

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VisualElement
    public class ShieldPowerUp
extends PowerUp
    The ShieldPowerUp is a power-up which gives the spaceship an extra shield. The spaceship can collide once with an obstacle without losing the game when this power-up is active.
